query:
INSERT INTO task_tags (task_id, tag_id)
            VALUES ($1, $2)
            ON CONFLICT (task_id, tag_id) DO UPDATE SET task_id = task_tags.task_id
            RETURNING
                id AS "id!: Uuid",
                task_id AS "task_id!: Uuid",
                tag_id AS "tag_id!: Uuid",
                created_at AS "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
